@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rmxddo(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.39 * v1 + 0.63)) * ((tmp + 0.65 - v0 + 0.16) / v2))
    tmp = (0.62 / 0.05)
    v0 = (0.02 + v1)
    v0 = (0.01 - wp.cos(wp.abs(v2 + 0.69)))
    tmp = wp.cos(0.18)
    v0 = 0.11
    v1 = (wp.cos(wp.abs(v2 + 0.25)) + 0.13)
    v0 = (wp.sin(wp.exp(tmp + 0.40)) + (wp.abs(tmp + 0.98) * wp.cos(v0 + 0.30)))
    data[tid] = v0
